<div class="story">
  <p>Nantucket Village is a water front condominium complex consisting of 12 individual buildings, each with 2 units in the smaller duplex style buildings and as many as 8 units in the larger buildings. There are a total of 44 individual units. </p><p>Situated on the Currituck Sound in the Southernmost end  of Duck and just north of <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/southern-shores/" title="Southern Shores">Southern Shores</a>, Nantucket Village is a short walk to down town Duck and  offers an indoor heated community pool, a tennis court, and sound access with a soundfront gazebo and dock. Located on some of the highest ground in Duck, some of the units offer spectacular water views. You can find Nantucket Village just south of the community of <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/duck/ocean-crest.asp" title="Oceancrest">Oceancrest</a>. </p>
